{"tid":509282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"平安夜鋸扒","createTime":"2017-12-25T06:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T07:31:26.000Z","uid":125470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"687f52292e389e01b3693a79d595085f51f58380","tid":509282,"uid":125470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"本來琴日平安夜 比條女話事揀去邊到食飯 今次仲要係我請 <br />\n<br />\n條仆街就揀左間好撚貴既西餐廳 我都唔撚識讀間餐廳既名 我見一塊死人扒都成幾百蚊 <br />\n<br />\n但見條女生日 好 今日我忍9你 <br />\n<br />\n入到去 我就同女朋友坐左係個卡位到 個WAITER(鬼佬)走埋黎問:what can I help you? <br />\n<br />\n雖然我英文真係中一二程度 不過喱句都唔算難到我 <br />\n<br />\n我女朋友用英文話 想要拎個MENU睇睇 <br />\n<br />\n由於入面全部英文我都唔多識 所以我就話跟女朋友點餐 佢要咩我要咩就算 <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬又走番埋黎問左句野 我剩係聽到:what xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx like? <br />\n<br />\n我女友就點左2個DINNER SPECIAL 之後個鬼佬又問:what xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx? <br />\n<br />\n我仍然係聽唔明 女友就同佢講:WELL DONE! <br />\n<br />\n我聽到喱到我大約就GET到 我估個鬼佬問佢覺得喱間餐廳既質素/員工服務/態度點 因為我見女友都讚佢 <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬轉另轉頭問我:whatxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx? <br />\n<br />\n我好自豪 充滿自信 大大聲答: GOOD JOB!! <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬就呆哂 唔明我無啦啦做乜講GOOD JOB咁 <br />\n<br />\n女友見到 即刻幫我答:WELL DONE <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬點點頭 就行左去 我其實到而家都唔明白 到底讚外國人係咪一定要用WELL DONE?"},{"pid":"dbe9cdb8eeab708d1936e38ad68773660655f6b8","tid":509282,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd245d7c053431cdf1c8ca99e0e49a4a2e6271bb","tid":509282,"uid":6675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"諗住入嚟睇jar jar 聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1497a3310452abd37b0664b6333453c66285513","tid":509282,"uid":125237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"This is fucking raw"},{"pid":"00c1b7e2d46fde6ce26ffc52ca5d13944aa891bd","tid":509282,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/151632_045c588fc21e0c5d5b346fc4ac2cc55e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F151632_045c588fc21e0c5d5b346fc4ac2cc55e.jpeg&h=41e19308&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2fc5976e5fda705ccbcbe2bba1995a1e629d17f","tid":509282,"uid":147086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:19:59.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"273380e74df2312c782c17d3c8bc5597a0e0e945","tid":509282,"uid":24216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"以為有巴士食扒相睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9afd6be103ce238b1e9ac937e63fd9e24ba4fe","tid":509282,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"又尋找新會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}